import React from 'react'
import{BrowerRouter as Router, Link, Switch, Route } from "react-router-dom"
import AddData from './AddData'
import ShowData from './showData'
//import Test from "./test";
import "./style.css"


const App = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Router>
            <Link to="/">Add Data</Link>
            <Link to="/show">Show Data</Link>
        </Router>
        <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/" component={AddData}></Route>
            <Route path="/show" component={ShowData}></Route>
        </Switch>
        <ShowData/>

        </>
    )
}

export default App
